            <title>[HBASE-12033] SecurityUtil#doAsLoginUser is absent in hadoop-1, making AccessController#postCreateTableHandler() ineffective</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-12033</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This affects build against hadoop-1 only.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From &lt;a href=&quot;https://builds.apache.org/job/HBase-0.98-on-Hadoop-1.1/497/testReport/junit/org.apache.hadoop.hbase.security.access/TestAccessController/testSplit/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://builds.apache.org/job/HBase-0.98-on-Hadoop-1.1/497/testReport/junit/org.apache.hadoop.hbase.security.access/TestAccessController/testSplit/&lt;/a&gt; :&lt;/p&gt;
